	<ThingDef MayRequire="vanillaracesexpanded.archon" ParentName="CGF1_MWP_BaseMakeableMeleeWeapon">
		<defName>CGF1_MWP_Archotanto</defName>
		<label>archotantō</label>
		<description>An ethereal weapon forged in the engimatic crucibles of an archotech. A fusion of unknown materials and arcane science, the Archotantō has the uncanny ability to phase through flesh, leaving behind agonizing scars by skipping tissue out of existence.\n\nArchotantōs amplify the psychic prowess of its bearer, resonating only with those who bear the archotech’s celestial touch. Archotantōs are often imbued with powerful psycasts, and are almost always wielded exclusively by the enigmatic archons.</description>
